            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublio</ex></expan> Aelio Peregri<lb break="no" n="2"/>no praesidi <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>prov</abbr><ex>inciae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Mauret</abbr><ex>aniae</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ariensis</ex></expan> perfec<lb break="no" n="5"/>tissimo viro <lb n="6"/>a <expan><abbr>cognitionib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>Aug<del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>gg</abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan></del> <expan><abbr>Tib</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audius</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>Licinius ex <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">p</supplied>raef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> I <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>aviae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Hisp</abbr><ex>anorum</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: Der Geehrte kam nach 203/204 n. Chr., zu welcher Zeit er noch als Prokurator der Mauretania Caesariensis bezeugt ist, als a cognitionibus nach Rom.</p>
            </div>
